Professional Summary
I am a dedicated and passionate Associate SRE/DevOps Engineer with a strong educational background and a wealth of certifications. My journey in the field of Information Technology began with a BSc. (Hons) in Information Technology, specializing in Software Engineering, and I have continued to expand my knowledge and skills ever since. My experience includes a successful internship in Site Reliability Engineering at Wiley Sri Lanka, where I honed my expertise in system administration and software development. I am proficient in a wide range of technologies, from Microsoft Azure and AWS Cloud to Docker, Kubernetes, and beyond. My commitment to excellence is reflected in my certifications, including Microsoft Certified: Azure Fundamentals and Scrum Foundation Professional Certificate. I am a proactive learner, a collaborative team player, and a creative problem-solver. I am excited to continue growing in my career and contributing to innovative, high-impact projects.
